items.preText:
Talha Khan: "Brendan Taylor is due for a big innings for a while now, ever since his return from england he has been timing the ball well but has failed to get a big score. Really looking forward to him scoring big today"

Istiak : "Bangladesh need to break this partnership, else both Williams & Taylor are more than capable to take the game away from BD. Come on Mashrafe make some changes to break the partnership "

suyog: "No worries Zimbabwe, these 2 can keep ticking till 40th over to get to 200, then, Raza, Moor and Chigumbara can take it further to 300 in last 10"
